text: Immerse yourself in the serene charm of this farmhouse nestled in a country setting, boasting a picturesque wraparound porch and tranquil pond views. Inside, a cozy living room beckons with a stone fireplace, perfect for gatherings. Discover culinary delights in the gourmet eat-in kitchen. The main floor offers a retreat with a primary bedroom & ensuite bath featuring a soaking tub, plus an adjacent office/den. Above the 3-car heated garage, a MIL suite awaits, complete with a kitchenette & private deck, overlooking the picturesque property. For equine enthusiasts, a horse arena adds to the allure of this idyllic retreat. Enjoy peace of mind with a Generac auto-start whole house generator, ensuring comfort & security no matter the weather.

Elegant English Colonial Revival Style is characterized by beautiful details of the Colonial era of homes. Located in the heart of DT Burlington. Historic design details feature an elegant double sided fireplace in living areas w/stunning tile & original light fixtures imported from Italy. Chefs kitchen with ample cabinet/counter space, tiled backsplash & granite. Light pouring in from all the original windows in the formal dining room add to the appeal. Tall ceilings throughout & original wood floors. This classy, elegant home was owned by a world renown doctor who made the space practical for any home/business life style. The spaces in this home flow w/ elegance & grace. Large shop/garage can fit 2 or more vehicles. Convenient location.

Wonderful newly refreshed home close to parks, schools and easy access to I-5. Brand new quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and new flooring throughout the home. Downstairs boasts tall 10-foot ceilings. Living room overlooks the fenced-in backyard that has been newly leveled and seeded for grass. Great size primary room with vaulted ceilings attached bathroom with double sinks and a walk-in closet. Home has a long driveway with plenty of parking and a 2-car attached garage.

Custom home built in 1993 by the current owners at The Pointe. Gorgeous views from every room in the home! Main level living with living room, formal dining room with built in cabinets, office with desks built in, wet bar, master bedroom with a fireplace, kitchen has a ton of cabinets that were custom built for this home, breakfast bar and breakfast table area. 3 car garage plus a good size shop with a view! So much parking area plus RV pad with dump and power. This is a home for entertaining! The quality of the build out is exceptional! Whole house fan, 2 septic tanks, gorgeous deck across the entire back of this home, storage galore, generator. This is a must see and the views are incredible!

Beautiful waterfront lot is now available for sale! Water, electric and high speed internet available. Glenhaven Lakes Club offers private heated pool, fully stocked fishing lake, boat ramp, clubhouse, tennis court and multiple private parks. Situated 20 minutes from either Bellingham or Burlington. Buyer to verify all the information.

Check out this Sedro-Woolley charmer just waiting for someone to give it a little TLC to freshen it up. Perfect for first time home buyers or as an investment. This home sits on a spacious lot just minutes from schools, parks and downtown. Don't miss out on this great opportunity. Estate Sale. Sold As-Is

Well-kept 3 bed 2.5 bath home located near the North Cascades National Park entrance. This tiny Pacific Northwest town makes up for its size with plenty of character, natural beauty, and recreation. Youll find easy-access community parks & hiking all surrounded by stunning mountain scenery. Situated on a large, fully fenced, full sun lot this home has vaulted ceilings, covered back patio, 2-car garage & more. All bedrooms on upper level are generously sized and get great natural light & air. Newer floors & paint. Primary bedroom with en-suite bathroom. Open kitchen & living room with sliders to back patio & yard are great for entertaining & relaxing. Additional parking for cars, boats, or RV with hookups near the yard with secure gate.

Welcome to your dream home in Sedro Woolley! This stunning 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath residence boasts 1, 822 sq ft of luxurious living space. The modern kitchen is a chef's delight with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops complemented by solid wood cabinets. Enjoy the warmth of a gas fireplace in the spacious living area. The main bedroom offers a private sanctuary with a balcony providing breathtaking views of the majestic mountains. Walk-in closets provide ample storage, ensuring a clutter-free environment. Conveniently located close to town, this home combines elegance and practicality for the perfect lifestyle. Freshly painted throughout and waiting for your touches! Don't miss the chance to make this gem yours!

Make your dreams come true! Nestled in on 1+ acres just outside Mt Vernon City limits, this beautiful 3 bedrm + office, 2 bath rambler boasts not only a 3-car attached garage, but a 24 x 30 shop with 100 amp service AND a 40 x 36 barn with 50 amp service and RV parking with RV drain! Bathed in natural light, this extremely well cared for home features a luxury kitchen with granite and Viking appliances, breakfast nook, formal dining room, beautiful pine wood ceilings, large laundry room, A/C, security system, 2 year new roof, hot tub, the list of features goes on and on. Gorgeous mature landscaping abundant with stunning color & beauty. Dont wait this is such a rare opportunity!

Welcome to Bucko Estates a new legacy community! This home is the Georgia plan with 3 bed/2 bath all on one level w/great curb appeal! There are almost $20K in upgrades. The great room has a gas fireplace & a vaulted ceiling. The great room, dining room & kitchen have LVP flooring. The kitchen has a gas range. The lower & 36 upper cabinets are alabaster color. The island is Ember color. The home has quartz countertops throughout the home! The carpet & lights are upgraded. The primary bedroom has a vaulted ceiling. The primary bath has a tile floor & tile shower, a freestanding tub, double sinks & walk in closet. There is a covered patio off of the dining room. The yard is fully landscaped & the backyard is fenced. 2 car + tandem garage.

Welcome to your new home in the heart of Sedro-Woolley! This great 4 bed, 2 bath gem boasts 2 living spaces, new HVAC (yes AC!) flooring, and a remodeled kitchen with quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances. Enjoy the luxury of remodeled bathrooms, a fully fenced yard with a huge storage shed, patio, water feature and fire pit to entertain guests. Plenty of parking in the driveway, including electric charging station & RV parking on the side. Experience comfort and convenience with this perfect blend of modern upgrades and prime location near all amenities.

The perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this two-story, four bedroom, 2.5 baths. Ideal for anyone wanting ample space. With the addition of a closet the den/office could become a fifth bedroom. The kitchen is designed for convenience, with lots of storage, a pantry, SS appliances and ample counterspace. A light bright dining room and separate laundry room enhance the comfort of this home. Double garage, and driveway provides plenty of parking for you and your guests. Outdoors is a fully fenced patio area with a gate to the community park. Community park offers walking trails, playground, basketball court, and RV parking!

Investment Opportunity-One Level Triplex. Well maintained & managed three unit '50's-built income property near park and Burlington-Edison High School. One duplex building has 2, 1 bedroom, 1 bath units, each 758SF w/carport & storage locker. Third unit is a free standing 996SF 1 bedroom, 1 bath w/carport & fireplace. Located on a nice corner lot that's over 11, 000 SF. Gas forced air heat, washer/dryer for each unit w/off street parking. Interiors are in good condition & nicely laid out for comfortable living. Currently a 6 CAP w/room for upside. Don't miss out on this incredible investment opportunity!

Farmington Square, a prestigious 55+ gated community in Burlington. Great location across from clubhouse, community garden & extra parking. Charming home with 3 bdrms, 1.75 baths, living rm w/vaulted ceiling & gas fireplace open to dining. Kitchen w/loads of cabinets, newer appliances, gas range & upgraded tile backsplash. Beautiful craftsmanship with high ceilings & trim provides a spacious feel & comfort throughout. Primary bdrm with walk-in shower & large walk-in closet. Spacious laundry room & pantry space. Deep single car garage attached w/storage cabinets & attic storage above. Exterior maintenance & landscaping included. Convenient location to town & I-5.

Move in ready Sedro Woolley rambler! Fully updated home features new interior/exterior paint, new LVP LifeProof flooring, new kitchen counters/cabinets/appliances, windows, trim, fixtures and more! Bonus room/office or possible 4th bedroom option. Primary bedroom with full on suite bath. Outside features a new fully fenced yard, garden area with blueberries and raspberries. Newly built 10'x20' storage shed with electricity and ample space for your hobbies or gardening. Metal 2 car car-port. Enjoy a back deck with 6 person hot tub. Located on a Cul-de-sac close to Hwy 9 and 20. Don't miss this wonderful home!

Welcome to your charming and well-appointed home in the perfect location! This remodeled mid-century gem in Old Town boasts classic details at every turn and has been freshly painted for a modern touch. The stylish kitchen will make doing dishes a pleasure, while the main level features 2 bedrooms, a full bath, hardwood floors, and a cozy gas fireplace. Downstairs, discover a spacious rec room, convenient 3/4 bath, a walk-in closet, and large storage/utility/laundry room with backyard access. Outside, the mature landscaping creates a serene oasis, perfect for entertaining in the amazing outdoor living spaces. And don't forget the detached 2-car garage with bonus shop a rare find! Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this home yours.
nearby_schools: Anacortes School District, Northwest Educational Service District 189

text: Indulge in the tranquility of waterfront living at this charming retreat on the shores of Dewey Beach. With breathtaking views of Whidbey, Hope & Skagit Islands complemented by majestic Cascade Range rising beyond the horizon. 2-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom home boasting oak floors, a bright sunroom, and expansive panoramic windows framing the stunning vistas. Spacious deck with built-in seating invites you to savor outdoor gatherings while soaking in the beauty of the surroundings. Explore the tidelands with your kayaks.100Ft of your own beach waterfront. A detached 2-car garage and workshop provide ample space for hobbies and storage. Whether you seek peaceful solitude or adventures, this coastal sanctuary promises an idyllic escape.

Look no further! You will love the many comforts of this fully updated rambler w/large SHOP & ADU. Welcoming covered front porch, open concept w/2 living areas, 4 bdrms, 2.5 baths in 2528 sq ft. The 1152 sq ft 3-bay garage/shop has room for all your toys! Efficient heat pump w/mini splits for heating/AC & wood burning stove. Gorgeous baths & kitchen; stainless, granite, tons of cabinets, island, bfast bar & dining rm. Primary suite has great closet space, hrdwd flrs, custom walkin surround shower & French doors to the large deck & fenced backyard. Guest bathroom includes laundry area & lots of storage. Modern flooring & lighting throughout. On the outskirts of town yet minutes to I-5 & all amenities. 5 minute stroll to Little Mountain Park!

A graceful and inviting atmosphere. Thoughtfully designed for easy living, tranquil evenings or lively gatherings. Take in the relaxing views of Skagit Bay, Whidbey Island and the Olympic Mountains from almost every room. Delight under your covered patio and enjoy the sights and sounds as if you are living in the country, welcome home. Floor-to-ceiling windows/doors that joyfully flood the space with natural light and frame the incredible views. Property is 2-parcels on over an acre of land. Irrigation system and 2-yard hydrants for easy watering. Spacious 3-car garage with 1 extra-deep bay. Built-in generator w/automatic transfer switch, powers most the home. Heat pump and forced air gas furnace, recirculation hot water pump, central vac.

Seize this rare chance to secure the final lot at gorgeous Creekside Meadows! This 1acre plot. 22979 Methow Court is more than land it's a chance to embrace a lifestyle highlighted by sweeping mountain and territorial views near Mount Vernon, blending rural charm with city convenience. This impressive community offers shared access to 68 acres of open space, perfect for nature enthusiasts. It comes utility-ready with PUD water, power, natural gas, septic design, and permitensuring a seamless build. Just 4 miles to I- 5, enjoy easy access to amenities while maintaining a serene lifestyle. Homes must be over 1800 sf, ensuring elegance. This is a rare opportunity to build in a premium picturesque setting of convenient country living.

Move in Ready! Bring your updates to this magnificent home located in a desirable neighborhood. This 4 bedroom, 3 bath, 2299sf home sits in the Hilltop Haven community. Home features hardwood floors, Crown Moulding, a Sunroom with a Northwestern view across the Skagit Valley. Included is a deck off back with a private backyard with fruit trees, a greenhouse and room for a garden. Gutters have installed a leaf and debris resistant system. Newer roof in great condition, sprinkler system, and a built-in home vacuum system located in the huge crawlspace. Don't forget to check out the 3-car garage, where one side was used as an office space. So much to offer and sits right on a Cul-de-sac and close to many community services.

This 3 bedroom, 1 3/4 bath home is an absolute jewel! There's not one thing that needs to be done before moving in - everything has been updated, painted, replaced and even the yard is newly landscaped. All appliances are high end and are included in sale.. A heat pump has been added for air conditioning. Back yard is fully fenced and has some lovely trees. Convenient location on Mount Vernon hill and just minutes away from all services. Perfect for first-time homebuyers or anyone looking to downsize or have single level living.
